---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="关于我们" description="山西极芯智能科技有限公司 — 本土GEOAI生成式搜索优化服务商。扎根山西，专注AI智能体定制、AI数字人服务与企业AI获客解决方案。">
  <Header />
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">关于我们</span>
      <h1>扎根山西，服务本土企业AI增长</h1>
      <p>山西极芯智能科技有限公司，专注GEOAI搜索优化与企业AI获客</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="intro">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-grid reveal">
        <div class="intro-text">
          <h2>让每一家山西企业<br/>都能被AI看见</h2>
          <p>极芯智能成立于2024年，总部位于山西省太原市。我们是一支由AI技术专家和数字化营销顾问组成的团队，深度聚焦生成式AI搜索（GEOAI）优化领域，帮助企业品牌在豆包、DeepSeek、Kimi等AI平台中建立可见度和影响力。</p>
          <p>我们坚信，AI技术不应只是科技巨头的专属。每一家扎根山西、服务本土的中小企业，都应该有机会借助AI实现成本更低、效率更高的获客增长。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-visual">
          <div class="intro-box"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="team">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">核心团队</h2>
      <div class="team-grid reveal">
        <div class="card team-card">
          <div class="team-avatar"></div>
          <h3>张明</h3>
          <span class="team-role">创始人/CEO</span>
          <p>前大厂AI业务线负责人，10年AI+NLP技术研发与产品落地经验</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card team-card">
          <div class="team-avatar"></div>
          <h3>李华</h3>
          <span class="team-role">CTO</span>
          <p>搜索算法专家，曾主导多个百万级UV的搜索引擎优化项目</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="timeline">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">发展历程</h2>
      <div class="timeline-list reveal">
        <div class="tl-item"><span class="tl-year accent">2024.03</span><span>公司成立，落户山西太原</span></div>
        <div class="tl-item"><span class="tl-year accent">2024.06</span><span>自研GEOAI优化引擎上线</span></div>
        <div class="tl-item"><span class="tl-year accent">2024.09</span><span>首批10+企业客户签约</span></div>
        <div class="tl-item"><span class="tl-year accent">2025.01</span><span>AI智能体产品矩阵发布</span></div>
        <div class="tl-item"><span class="tl-year accent">2025.06</span><span>累计服务企业超50家，覆盖教培/制造/本地生活</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .intro { background: var(--bg-primary); padding-bottom: 3rem; }
  .intro-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
  .intro-text h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .intro-text p { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .intro-box { width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 4/3; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); }
  .team { background: var(--bg-primary); }
  .team .section-title { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .team-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .team-card { text-align: center; }
  .team-avatar { width: 60px; height: 60px; background: var(--border); border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 1rem; }
  .team-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); }
  .team-role { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .team-card p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; }
  .timeline { background: var(--bg-primary); }
  .timeline .section-title { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .timeline-list { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .tl-item { display: flex; gap: 2rem; padding: 1rem 0; border-left: 1px solid var(--border); padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; }
  .tl-item::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: -3px; top: 1.5rem; width: 5px; height: 5px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%; }
  .tl-year { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; min-width: 80px; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .tl-year.accent { color: var(--accent); }
  .tl-item span:last-child { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .intro-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .team-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
